snippet.title: soul Interface | A Modest Teaser
snippet.description:
soul Interface is a virtual aquarium / 
ecosystem simulator
that allows players to design artificial lifeforms, train their AI to survive, compete, and cooperate in a virtual physics-based environment.

Wishlist it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2878890/soul_Interface/?beta=1
Join our discord: https://discord.gg/VCr4hnHQvK
